00139 netsnmp_container *
00140 netsnmp_container_get_null(void)
00141 {
00142     /*
00143      * allocate memory
00144      */
00145     netsnmp_container *c;
00146     DEBUGMSGTL(("container:null:get_null","in\n"));
00147     c = SNMP_MALLOC_TYPEDEF(netsnmp_container);
00148     if (NULL==c) {
00149         snmp_log(LOG_ERR, "couldn't allocate memory\n");
00150         return NULL;
00151     }
00152 
00153     c->container_data = NULL;
00154         
00155     c->get_size = _null_size;
00156     c->init = _null_init;
00157     c->cfree = _null_free;
00158     c->insert = _null_insert;
00159     c->remove = _null_remove;
00160     c->find = _null_find;
00161     c->find_next = _null_find_next;
00162     c->get_subset = _null_get_subset;
00163     c->get_iterator = NULL; /* _null_iterator; */
00164     c->for_each = _null_for_each;
00165     c->clear = _null_clear;
00166        
00167     return c;
00168 }
